                    <span>This an excellent "crash course" on the wireless industry. Written with a very high level of knowledge without confusing, as is so often the case. Great library addition.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Easy to Navigate; Written in Plain English</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
