                      <span>3</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-06-05</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book covers all the main topics as an introduction to the wireless industry. It's layout is excellent and easy to navigate. Foremost, the book is written in plain english and contains lots of diagrams for those who think visually.<p>Last of all, when addressing more complex topics in detail, it contains just enough repetition of the fundamental issues that the repetition enforces what you've learned in earlier chapters. Great bookself source for investment analysts trying to get up to speed on the industry quickly.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Solid time & money investment</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
